Titolo: Endless Ocean

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Endless Ocean (known as Forever Blue in Japan) is a scuba diving adventure game for the Wii. It is published by Nintendo and was developed by Arika, who also worked on their spiritual predecessor Everblue, another scuba diving adventure game. It was released in Japan on August 2, 2007, in Europe on November 9, 2007, and in North America on January 21, 2008 â€“ after it had been planned for an October 2007 release.
A sequel entitled Endless Ocean 2: Adventures of the Deep was released in Japan on September 17, 2009, Europe on February 5, 2010, and North America on February 22, 2010, with the title Endless Ocean: Blue World.

Genere: Non specificato


